				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> the combat guardian has a creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei]{Grabbed}</p><hr /><p>The combat guardian attempts to drag closer the target towards them. Attempt an @Check[athletics|against:fortitude] check against the target's fortitude dc.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> the target is [[/act reposition]]{Repositioned} by 10 feet towards the combat guardian.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> the target is [[/act reposition]]{Repositioned} by 5 feet towards the combat guardian.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> the target manages to break free from the Grab</p>",
